WELCOME HOME

Welcome to Echuca and an experience like no other! Our bakery here offers both upstairs and downstairs as well as indoor and outdoor seating, overlooking the calm and serene surroundings of the Campaspe river. And in addition to the visual feast, let us also entice your senses with our yummo coffee and delectable cakes and pastries. Come and kick back, relax and enjoy the warm personalised service from our friendly team. Immerse yourself in the atmosphere with friends or family, while listening to one our popular local bands, every Sunday around lunch time. Now, that’s how life was meant to be…

KYLIE DIVOLA

our bakery manager in Echuca
